quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Woe to every slanderer and defamer
  104,2,who amasses wealth and keeps on counting it
  104,3,He thinks that his wealth will insure his status forever
  104,4,By no means! He shall be thrown into Hotamah
  104,5,What will make you understand what Hotamah is
  104,6,It is the fire kindled to a blaze by Allah Himself
  104,7,The one which will rise right to the hearts
  104,8,closing in upon them from every side
  104,9,in outstretched columns